These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, architect, photographer, mechanic
1. the mechanic is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
2. the police-officer is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
3. the architect is not to the left of the photographer##8
4. the architect is on the left of the mechanic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Job   | photographer | architect | mechanic | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite, fanta, coffee
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
2. the person drinking sprite is between the person drinking coffee and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | fanta | sprite | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, watermelon, artichoke, banana
1. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
2. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the person eating banana##1
3. the person eating watermelon is not to the left of the person eating banana##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |   2   |   3    |   4    |
| Food   | lettuce | banana | watermelon | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving, singing, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##8
3. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Hobby   | skydiving | hiking | singing | puzzles |

 #################################

 
