2. the person eating radish is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating radish is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
4. the person eating radish is the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |     3     |   4   |
| Food   | cranberry | zucchini | radish | carrot |

